### [ATTACK] Cancel — SQL injection in reason
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{activeSubId}}/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "reason": "'; UPDATE \"Subscription\" SET status='ACTIVE' WHERE '1'='1",
  "cancel_at_period_end": false
}

